 <h2>What are packages</h2>

 	We don't usually store all of our files on our computer in the same location. We use a well-organized hierarchy of directories for easier access.
    A package is basically a directory with Python files and a file with the name _init.py. This means that every directory inside of the Python path, which contains a file named __init_.py, will be treatedâ€¦